1
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,810
Why are you running around?

2
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:56,360
Your Highness, rest assured.

3
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:57,690
Everything is in place.

4
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:02,650
I won't ever see that low-down servant again, will I?

5
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:04,720
I promise

6
00:02:05,440 --> 00:02:07,160
she won’t bother you again.

7
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:13,680
Why do you choose to deliver the powder on the day of the tea party?

8
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:17,120
The shell powder is washed with dye.

9
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,640
Only a little dye is used

10
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,680
so that no one can find out.

11
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:25,420
It takes several months of poison accumulation

12
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,480
to produce actual symptoms.

13
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:31,090
But Consort Yu has been suffering abdominal pain

14
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,560
and asked the imperial doctors for help

15
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,360
after using it for about one month.

16
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:36,360
She's making such grand movements.

17
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:39,600
Don't you find it unnatural?

18
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,960
You mean…

19
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:46,079
Her Majesty has developed a close relationship with Palace of Eternal Peace.

20
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:49,540
And Wei Yingluo has been delivering pearl powder frequently.

21
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:52,320
They may have found it.

22
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,800
They are probably setting a trap

23
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:56,320
to catch us on spot.

24
00:02:57,680 --> 00:03:01,540
But the fetus may have been affected by the mental trauma of Consort Yu

25
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,080
and it could be true.

26
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,730
Are you sure about this?

27
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:09,200
You may be oversensitive.

28
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:11,120
I…

29
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,920
I’m not sure.

30
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,240
But the best way

31
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:19,160
is check the medical records of Consort Yu at the Imperial Hospital.

32
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,820
We surely can see the problem.

33
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,480
If the medical records differ from what Fangcao said,

34
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:25,160
they are trying to trap us.

35
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:30,400
What is your plan

36
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,160
if you guessed it right?

37
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,160
I heard

38
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:38,160
Her Majesty trusts Wei Yingluo a lot.

39
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:41,840
She gave her the task

40
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,050
of taking care of the lychee trees.

41
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:47,040
Your Highness, don't you hate her very much?

42
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,680
I have an idea

43
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:51,400
to get rid of her.

44
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:55,280
It can also humiliate Her Majesty

45
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,920
and ruin her prestige.

46
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,600
What should we do?

47
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,160
What should we do?

48
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,440
What happened?

49
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,130
The lock got pried open.

50
00:04:18,269 --> 00:04:19,440
The lychee trees

51
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:22,360
are killed by hot water.

52
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,560
Yingluo,

53
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,960
what should we do?

54
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:27,690
Yingluo,

55
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,010
where are you going?

56
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:33,400
Greetings to you, Your Majesty.

57
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,200
Forego the formalities.

58
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,400
Take a seat.

59
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:48,290
Your hands are cold,

60
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,720
Your Majesty?

61
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:52,980
Have you not fully recovered?

62
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,600
Or your servants

63
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:57,090
are tiring you too much?

64
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:00,600
Your Majesty,

65
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,900
it has nothing to do with them.

66
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:06,240
I've always had cold hands and feet.

67
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:08,600
An imperial doctor has made me a prescription.

68
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:12,120
Consort Chun has also gave me a medicinal bath to dip my hands and feet in.

69
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:14,360
They just don’t work.

70
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,960
The imperial doctors in the Palace

71
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,320
are highly-skilled,

72
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,360
but they are too conservative

73
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,720
and stick to old rules.

74
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,760
If they are too careful in medicine application,

75
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,290
how can they cure diseases?

76
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:31,960
A few days ago, Fuheng said

77
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:34,080
Jiangsu had a famous doctor named Doctor Nanyang.

78
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:36,080
He has divine-like medical skills.

79
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:38,340
No diseases are incurable to him.

80
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:40,159
I've sent someone for him.

81
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:41,960
They’ll take him to the capital as soon as possible.

82
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:44,159
By then, I'll let him nurse your health.

83
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:46,290
Thank you for your care, Your Majesty.

84
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,040
Yingluo,

85
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,680
let's report it to Her Majesty.

86
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,640
Can't you see His Majesty is there too?

87
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:56,400
His Majesty?

88
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,560
So what?

89
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:01,640
The tribute of Fujian got totally destroyed.

90
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:02,520
Were you him,

91
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:03,890
would you get angry?

92
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,600
Yes, absolutely.

93
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,220
He might have us beheaded.

94
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,760
Someone destroyed the lychee trees

95
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:10,760
to frame us.

96
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,560
What should we do now?

97
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,920
What to do? What to do?

98
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:16,920
Of course

99
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,480
we'll fight back.

100
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,040
Now,

101
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:23,960
listen carefully.

102
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:28,200
Choose the lychees that are still acceptable.

103
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,880
Send them to the Royal Restaurant,

104
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:31,210
and tell the Restaurant

105
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,560
Her Majesty is having a lychee party.

106
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,680
Ask them to immediately think of a way.

107
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,120
Consort Chun.

108
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,840
Afterwards, tell Her Majesty

109
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:38,560
the lychees from two trees are made into food.

110
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,440
The fruit of the remaining tree is left to be picked on spot.

111
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:41,300
Picked on spot?

112
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,320
No.

113
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,680
That’s why we will get found out.

114
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,960
Her Majesty said

115
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:49,360
she’d pick lychees for His Majesty with her own hands.

116
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,159
She can't casually take it back.

117
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,720
One of the trees must be brought to the party.

118
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,520
Of course,

119
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,600
we must have a plan.

120
00:06:58,840 --> 00:06:59,880
What plan?

121
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,160
Consort Xian,

122
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:12,960
on my last birthday,

123
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:15,620
you gave me a pair of jade ruyi.

124
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:17,800
After checking them several times,

125
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,860
I couldn't notice anything unusual.

126
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,840
Erqing pointed it out

127
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,680
Heart Sutra

128
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,200
was carved on their handles.

129
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,440
Afterwards, an imperial doctor told me

130
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:31,600
your finger got injured

131
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,520
when you carved them.

132
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:36,880
I feel guilty about it.

133
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:39,080
I just exerted my measly effort

134
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:40,840
to celebrate your birthday.

135
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,880
I wish Your Majesty good health,

136
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,970
and a peaceful and smooth life.

137
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,200
Erqing.

138
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,480
Your Majesty,

139
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,120
I've said

140
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,440
I will choose a favorite

141
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,290
among all my birthday gifts

142
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:57,400
and then reward the person who gave it.

143
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,720
However,

144
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:01,520
your gift

145
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:05,400
is the most unique one.

146
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,680
Yet I can’t reward you

147
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:08,620
because you own the whole nation.

148
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:12,240
So I want to give this reward to Consort Xian.

149
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,120
What do you think?

150
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,120
Your Majesty,

151
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,520
I don't deserve it.

152
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,120
The reward of Her Majesty

153
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:33,760
shows her appreciation of your sincerity.

154
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,260
You mustn't refuse it.

155
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,260
Thank you for your reward, Your Majesty.

156
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,480
I will accept it.

157
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:49,720
Rise, please.

158
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:01,880
Trying to win people's hearts, and fishing for fame.

159
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,840
Pretentious.

160
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,280
Get it back.

161
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,360
Yingluo,

162
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,000
will this work?

163
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,120
Of course not.

164
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:40,840
No?

165
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:42,880
Guard here.

166
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,480
You must not leave here.

167
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,290
Nor let anyone get near.

168
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:50,220
Go there when it's time to offer the lychees.

169
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,560
Are we clear?

170
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:55,960
But...

171
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:07,080
Consort,

172
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:09,780
Her Majesty is holding a lychee party today.

173
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:12,720
If you keep hiding here and refusing to see people,

174
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,360
Her Majesty may feel hurt.

175
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:16,920
Look at me.

176
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:21,400
I’d better not spoil the joy of everyone.

177
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:23,000
All the concubines have gone there,

178
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,120
except you.

179
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,680
If some vicious people learn of it,

180
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:28,680
they'll say you are being proud

181
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,360
because of your pregnancy.

182
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,440
I said I won't go.

183
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,700
Can't you understand?

184
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:35,840
Yingluo.

185
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:43,340
What are you doing?

186
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:46,860
I'm here to invite Consort Yu to attend the lychee banquet.

187
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,400
Even you are being hard on me?

188
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:56,500
You know that I'm afraid of seeing those people.

189
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,160
I don't want to go.

190
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,960
I don't want to see Consort Jia,

191
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,400
or Noble Consort Gao.

192
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,000
Leave us alone.

193
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,580
What are you doing?

194
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,780
Aren't you afraid?

195
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:26,720
Once you're dead, everything will be over.

196
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,280
No one will try to harm you again.

197
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:29,120
Yingluo...

198
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:30,200
Consort Yu,

199
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,340
Noble Consort Gao and Consort Jia

200
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:34,240
tried to harm you repeatedly.

201
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:37,340
You think you'll be safe if you hide here?

202
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:38,800
The more you're afraid of trouble,

203
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:40,400
the more they will bully you.

204
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:42,880
Think about the tragic death of Consort Yi.

205
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:45,210
Think about how you almost got strangled.

206
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:48,480
This palace is not a safe harbor.

207
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,160
It's just a tomb

208
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:51,840
that can be sealed anytime!

209
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,760
It has buried Consort Yi.

210
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,920
The next one

211
00:11:58,280 --> 00:11:59,040
will be you.

212
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:06,240
You're right.

213
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:09,840
I'm afraid.

214
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:13,200
I'm so afraid.

215
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:18,280
Every time I think about those people,

216
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:20,160
and what they did,

217
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,880
I tremble with fear.

218
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,320
But Yingluo,

219
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,040
I had fought.

220
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,440
You saw what happened

221
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,400
to Sister Consort Yi.

222
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:39,280
Consort Yu,

223
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,520
when I was eight,

224
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:42,890
I got bitten by a bad dog.

225
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:46,480
It was so painful that I cried a whole night.

226
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:49,480
The next day, I took a rod

227
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:52,020
and chased after that bad dog.

228
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,880
I chased it across half of the capital city.

229
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,800
In face of bad dogs,

230
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,680
you must be braver

231
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,400
and fiercer,

232
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,460
so you can scare them away.

233
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,840
With the same reasoning,

234
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:07,440
evil people bully the weak but fear the strong.

235
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:08,770
The more you are afraid,

236
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,640
the more they will bully you.

237
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,400
For your child,

238
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,840
for poor Consort Yi,

239
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,000
pick up your weapons

240
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:24,360
and face your enemies.

241
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:28,200
Weapons.

242
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:29,680
Me?

243
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:34,240
What weapon do I have?

244
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,560
Your weakness,

245
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,880
your tears,

246
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:42,960
the Emperor’s offspring in your belly,

247
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:45,840
are all your weapons.

248
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:49,560
If you want to fight back,

249
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:53,160
today is your best chance.

250
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:12,960
Your Majesty,

251
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:17,180
this is "White Snow and Red Plum" specially made by the Royal Restaurant.

252
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:21,040
The Royal Restaurant really toiled for this.

253
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:24,360
They look elegant.

254
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,640
Your Majesty,

255
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:27,200
lychees can cause excessive internal heat.

256
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:29,130
So they soaked them in salted water

257
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:32,130
and paired them with wolfberry for neutralization.

258
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:38,720
Lychees used in food are nothing special.

259
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:42,000
After all, dried lychees are sent here every year.

260
00:14:42,680 --> 00:14:45,140
If you add other ingredients to the lychees,

261
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:50,680
they won’t taste right.

262
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:53,160
People who know lychees

263
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:55,640
are only interested in the fresh ones.

264
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:58,640
Your Majesty,

265
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:02,720
didn't you say you’d pick the fruit today?

266
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:06,200
Why can’t I see anything happening?

267
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,200
Where's Yingluo?

268
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,160
She...

269
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:14,240
Where

270
00:15:15,280 --> 00:15:16,600
is Yingluo now?

271
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:22,320
Your Majesty, Yingluo…

272
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,840
Consort Yu is here!

273
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:33,360
Consort Yu.

274
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:45,160
I am late.

275
00:15:45,400 --> 00:15:47,920
May Your Majesties forgive me.

276
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:48,880
Consort Yu,

277
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:50,440
you're here.

278
00:15:50,640 --> 00:15:51,880
Rise, please.

279
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:57,560
Your Majesty, you’re holding a party.

280
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:59,480
I should come.

281
00:16:00,160 --> 00:16:01,720
And you are so caring.

282
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:04,040
I have no reason to be idling around.

283
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,240
Consort Yu,

284
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:07,850
how are you feeling?

285
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:10,560
Thank you for your concerns, Your Majesty.

