Snowball.

570
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:46,000
I decided on my own.

571
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:48,120
May Your Majesty forgive me.

572
00:29:53,040 --> 00:29:54,480
Yingluo, oh, Yingluo.

573
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:57,720
How could you think of such an idea!

574
00:30:02,800 --> 00:30:04,080
Noble Consort Gao

575
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:06,920
used Snowball to scare Consort Yu.

576
00:30:08,080 --> 00:30:10,840
Her outstanding debt was paid today.

577
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:13,640
We were not aggrieving her.

578
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:17,680
It's nothing for me to admit my mistake and accept punishment.

579
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:20,000
Noble Consort Gao and Consort Jia did that

580
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:22,200
to embarrass Your Majesty.

581
00:30:22,360 --> 00:30:23,960
How could I let them succeed?

582
00:30:26,120 --> 00:30:28,120
I failed to watch the trees properly

583
00:30:28,520 --> 00:30:30,000
and the lychees were destroyed.

584
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,320
That’s huge.

585
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:33,320
But Noble Consort Gao

586
00:30:33,480 --> 00:30:35,680
instigated that bad dog to harm Consort Yu,

587
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,920
and destroyed tribute of Fujian

588
00:30:36,920 --> 00:30:38,360
to spoil your banquet.

589
00:30:39,080 --> 00:30:40,940
My crime was much minor than hers.

590
00:30:43,360 --> 00:30:45,160
Consort Yu kept shouting

591
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,330
and demanding justice.

592
00:30:48,040 --> 00:30:50,760
His Majesty was too busy to notice your mistake.

593
00:30:51,560 --> 00:30:54,620
He focused his attention on Noble Consort Gao instead.

594
00:30:55,600 --> 00:30:56,680
But Yingluo,

595
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:58,680
you told me

596
00:30:59,360 --> 00:31:00,820
that you didn't read much.

597
00:31:01,560 --> 00:31:04,840
How did you reply His Majesty's question?

598
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:08,920
The tiger and the rhinoceros got out of their cages,

599
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:10,600
and the tortoise shell and jade offerings got destroyed in their containers.

600
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:11,680
Who is to blame?

601
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:14,300
Your Majesty, you mean these sentences?

602
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:16,440
His Majesty said it too fast.

603
00:31:16,840 --> 00:31:18,700
I didn’t understand immediately

604
00:31:19,720 --> 00:31:22,320
that His Majesty was calling to account.

605
00:31:23,320 --> 00:31:24,360
Your Majesty,

606
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:26,000
I only know three sentences

607
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:28,000
recorded in Analects of Confucius.

608
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:30,120
"Is it not pleasant to learn

609
00:31:30,360 --> 00:31:32,000
with a constant perseverance and application?"

610
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:33,400
"When I walk along with two others,

611
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:35,460
I surely will learn from one of them."

612
00:31:36,600 --> 00:31:37,720
And lastly,

613
00:31:38,280 --> 00:31:39,520
“The tiger and the rhinoceros got out of their cages,

614
00:31:39,520 --> 00:31:40,640
and the tortoise shell and jade offerings got destroyed in their containers.

615
00:31:40,640 --> 00:31:41,720
Who is to blame?”

616
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:43,240
I heard those three sentences

617
00:31:43,240 --> 00:31:45,800
when my neighbor, a scholar, recited them.

618
00:31:46,080 --> 00:31:48,160
Then I guessed the meaning.

619
00:31:50,080 --> 00:31:50,880
Yingluo,

620
00:31:52,800 --> 00:31:54,060
you are quick-witted.

621
00:31:55,320 --> 00:31:56,120
It's just that

622
00:31:57,560 --> 00:32:00,160
you were not well educated when you were young.

623
00:32:00,560 --> 00:32:02,290
I came from an ordinary family.

624
00:32:02,600 --> 00:32:06,000
A full meal and warm clothes are already great fortune for us.

625
00:32:06,280 --> 00:32:08,880
How could I have the luxurious hope of reading?

626
00:32:09,560 --> 00:32:10,360
Your Majesty,

627
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:14,520
most women in this empire are like me.

628
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:20,440
From tomorrow,

629
00:32:21,280 --> 00:32:22,480
I will teach you.

630
00:32:24,560 --> 00:32:25,480
Your Majesty?

631
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,290
You're so intelligent.

632
00:32:29,040 --> 00:32:32,300
I'll teach you to read books and know the proper etiquette.

633
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:35,280
We must not waste the talent and intelligence

634
00:32:35,280 --> 00:32:37,880
endowed by the heaven.

635
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:40,880
Thank you, Your Majesty!

636
00:32:58,280 --> 00:32:59,610
Imperial Consort Xian.

637
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:02,360
You told Her Majesty that I urgently needed money,

638
00:33:02,360 --> 00:33:03,840
am I right?

639
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:06,520
Yes.

640
00:33:07,160 --> 00:33:08,240
Why did you do that?

641
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:10,800
I mentioned it as some idle gossip.

642
00:33:10,800 --> 00:33:12,560
I didn’t mean anything.

643
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,840
I didn’t expect she’d remember it

644
00:33:14,840 --> 00:33:16,760
and grant you a gift today.

645
00:33:20,840 --> 00:33:21,680
I know

646
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:24,240
you don’t want to be associated with me.

647
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:26,840
But today, let me tell you some sincere words.

648
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:30,760
Her Majesty has never meant to gang up.

649
00:33:31,640 --> 00:33:34,160
She never wants anyone to repay her kindness, either.

650
00:33:34,160 --> 00:33:35,720
She just helped you

651
00:33:36,120 --> 00:33:37,880
because she heard that you were in trouble.

652
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:40,440
She was afraid her help might be a mental burden.

653
00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:42,520
So she made an excuse for rewarding you.

654
00:33:42,520 --> 00:33:45,080
She specially did it in front of His Majesty to make it more legitimate.

655
00:33:45,080 --> 00:33:47,240
This money is now officially yours.

656
00:33:48,360 --> 00:33:49,960
No one will comment about it.

657
00:33:52,560 --> 00:33:53,280
Sister,

658
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:56,400
you can go save your brother with the money.

659
00:34:07,880 --> 00:34:08,520
Empress,

660
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,409
you're assured now, right?

661
00:34:13,150 --> 00:34:14,000
Why?

662
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:15,760
Are you still suspicious

663
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,290
of Her Majesty' intention?

664
00:34:17,560 --> 00:34:19,560
I never suspected Her Majesty.

665
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:21,880
If she had wanted to oblige me,

666
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:24,840
she could have summoned me to Palace of Eternal Spring.

667
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:27,710
Today she rewarded me in a perfectly justifiable name,

668
00:34:27,710 --> 00:34:30,170
because she didn't want me to feel burdened.

669
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:32,400
But Consort Chun…

670
00:34:34,520 --> 00:34:36,320
What's wrong with Consort Chun?

671
00:34:36,600 --> 00:34:38,280
Consort Chun is very sharp-minded.

672
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:40,190
She knew I wouldn't accept the money,

673
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:41,560
so she told Her Majesty.

674
00:34:42,630 --> 00:34:43,670
This way,

675
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:45,560
I have to accept this favor of hers,

676
00:34:45,560 --> 00:34:46,820
even if I don't want to.

677
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:48,710
Empress,

678
00:34:49,120 --> 00:34:50,360
I don’t understand.

679
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:53,130
I only know that Young Master can be saved now.

680
00:34:54,190 --> 00:34:54,880
Alright.

681
00:34:55,600 --> 00:34:56,480
This being the case,

682
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:58,340
I can only repay the favor slowly.

683
00:34:58,680 --> 00:35:01,400
Deliver the silver out of the Palace as soon as possible.

684
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:02,240
Yes.

685
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:14,680
Eunuch Li.

686
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,400
Guard Suolun.

687
00:35:16,560 --> 00:35:17,690
His Majesty ordered

688
00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:20,120
this dog be killed.

689
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:24,600
We are all His Majesty's close attendants.

690
00:35:24,600 --> 00:35:25,600
If we get blood on us

691
00:35:25,600 --> 00:35:27,320
it may affect the fortune of His Majesty.

692
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:29,120
It's best for you guards to do it.

693
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:30,280
Eunuch Li!

694
00:35:37,720 --> 00:35:38,880
Get blood on them!

695
00:35:39,360 --> 00:35:42,420
You’re worried Noble Consort Gao might come after you.

696
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,600
Go patrol elsewhere.

697
00:35:58,120 --> 00:35:59,160
Guard Suolun.

698
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:00,280
You are…?

699
00:36:02,160 --> 00:36:04,360
The maid in Palace of Eternal Peace.

700
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:06,930
I am a palace maid of Palace of Eternal Spring.

701
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:07,880
Yeah.

702
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:09,280
Your name is Wei Yingluo.

703
00:36:09,520 --> 00:36:10,320
That time

704
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:12,400
you were so ruthless with that eunuch!

705
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:13,600
I'll never forget it.

706
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:14,520
I had no choice.

707
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,080
I had to protect myself.

708
00:36:16,080 --> 00:36:17,740
May you understand, Officer.

709
00:36:18,160 --> 00:36:19,240
I am here today

710
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:21,280
to take Snowball.

711
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:23,120
It hurt Consort Yu,

712
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:25,130
ruined Her Majesty’s banquet,

713
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:27,320
and caused me to be punished.

714
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:29,400
Take it to Palace of Eternal Spring?

715
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:30,880
What are you going to do with it?

716
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:32,410
First, I will vent my anger,

717
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,320
then I'll kill it.

718
00:36:35,600 --> 00:36:36,880
You young lady

719
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:38,360
can do that?

720
00:36:39,680 --> 00:36:41,010
That’s funny, Officer.

721
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,440
This dog

722
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:44,640
almost killed me.

723
00:36:45,560 --> 00:36:47,620
Though I managed to keep my position,

724
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:49,930
I got harshly scolded by my master.

725
00:36:50,600 --> 00:36:51,880
If I don't skin it!

726
00:36:52,520 --> 00:36:53,200
Fine.

727
00:36:53,200 --> 00:36:54,260
I'll give it to you.

728
00:36:59,640 --> 00:37:00,160
Wait.

729
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:03,080
What is it?

730
00:37:04,040 --> 00:37:05,970
If His Majesty asks about it later?

731
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:07,420
Don't worry, Officer.

732
00:37:07,640 --> 00:37:09,040
You’ll have the evidence

733
00:37:09,400 --> 00:37:10,640
to report on your mission.

734
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:11,200
Alright.

735
00:37:11,200 --> 00:37:12,000
That's a deal.

736
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:24,360
How dare you!

737
00:37:24,520 --> 00:37:25,840
You passed off your duty?

738
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:27,600
She asked for it.

739
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:29,130
I didn’t force it to her.

740
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:30,240
Don't pretend.

741
00:37:30,720 --> 00:37:32,000
You were worried Noble Consort Gao

742
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,240
would understand what happened,

743
00:37:33,240 --> 00:37:35,370
and ask about how her beloved dog died.

744
00:37:35,680 --> 00:37:37,120
She can't do anything to His Majesty

745
00:37:37,120 --> 00:37:38,720
but she can deal with a guard.

746
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:41,880
A woman's hatred is the most horrible thing.

747
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:43,400
It's best not to get it.

748
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:45,800
Then you just pushed it onto Wei Yingluo?

749
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:47,520
She's a palace maid of Palace of Eternal Spring.

750
00:37:47,520 --> 00:37:49,880
Palace of Eternal Spring and Palace of Gathered Elegance have always been enemies.

751
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:52,280
More hatred isn't anything to be scared of.

752
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:54,560
I’m worried she couldn’t do it.

753
00:37:54,960 --> 00:37:56,290
She's a girl, after all.

754
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:59,260
Maybe you have underestimated Wei Yingluo.

755
00:38:24,320 --> 00:38:25,920
Your Majesty, what's wrong?

756
00:38:26,520 --> 00:38:27,380
It's not right.

757
00:38:28,200 --> 00:38:29,240
What's not right?

758
00:38:32,560 --> 00:38:35,560
Do you remember how that lychee tree looked at the end?

759
00:38:36,600 --> 00:38:38,460
I don't understand what you mean.

760
00:38:39,040 --> 00:38:42,100
That lychee tree was destroyed by Snowball, wasn't it?

761
00:38:42,240 --> 00:38:44,840
The lychees on the lower part could be destroyed.

762
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:46,440
But those on the higher part?

763
00:38:47,120 --> 00:38:47,880
They…

764
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:56,840
Go to Palace of Eternal Spring right away

765
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:58,100
and bring me that maid.

766
00:38:58,600 --> 00:38:59,880
I am going to punish her!

767
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:00,560
Yes.

768
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:06,120
Wait.

769
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:08,400
Come back.

770
00:39:11,400 --> 00:39:12,200
Your Majesty.

771
00:39:13,400 --> 00:39:14,400
No need to go.

772
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,620
Your Majesty, you...?

773
00:39:17,400 --> 00:39:18,800
That audacious girl!

774
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,660
She redirected the disaster.

775
00:39:22,560 --> 00:39:24,400
What's the use of going there now?

776
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:26,000
The dust is settled already.

777
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:27,880
Your Majesty, that’s why

778
00:39:28,560 --> 00:39:30,200
we can't spare that maid.

779
00:39:30,280 --> 00:39:32,320
I will go and bring her here from Palace of Eternal Spring immediately!

780
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:33,360
For what? Bring!

781
00:39:35,200 --> 00:39:38,160
I just finished punishing Consort Jia and Noble Consort Gao.

782
00:39:38,160 --> 00:39:40,280
Then in less than four hours I retract my order?

783
00:39:40,280 --> 00:39:41,410
Who do you think I am?

784
00:39:42,520 --> 00:39:43,320
Your Majesty,

785
00:39:43,640 --> 00:39:44,970
then you don't blame her

786
00:39:45,200 --> 00:39:47,800
for framing Noble Consort Gao and Consort Jia?

787
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,600
Consort Yu was shivering.

788
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:52,900
I’m sure Palace of Gathered Elegance

789
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:56,200
have done something to the lychees and Consort Yu.

790
00:39:57,760 --> 00:39:58,760
Now,

791
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:02,170
they are suffering for their own actions.

792
00:40:03,160 --> 00:40:06,360
Your Majesty, you are going to let her go?

793
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:10,880
That maid made every effort

794
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:13,560
to protect Her Majesty.

795
00:40:15,120 --> 00:40:16,760
I can't be too harsh

796
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,880
for Her Majesty’s sake.

797
00:40:21,040 --> 00:40:22,200
But she used my hand

798
00:40:23,120 --> 00:40:24,840
to take her revenge.

799
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:27,160
Despicable.

800
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:29,560
So despicable.

801
00:40:36,520 --> 00:40:37,450
Chamberlain Li,

802
00:40:37,800 --> 00:40:38,840
what's wrong?

803
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:40,360
Desheng,

804
00:40:41,040 --> 00:40:41,960
what do you think of His Majesty

805
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:44,520
most of the time?

806
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:46,280
Diligent in governing and loving his people?

807
00:40:46,280 --> 00:40:47,960
No, I don't mean that.

808
00:40:48,760 --> 00:40:49,720
Then

809
00:40:51,200 --> 00:40:52,480
determined and decisive.

810
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:53,200
Yes.

811
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:55,520
Who is His Majesty?

812
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:57,660
The Emperor of Great Qing.

813
00:40:57,840 --> 00:40:59,080
The master of the nation.

814
00:40:59,080 --> 00:41:00,040
He can kill anyone he dislikes

815
00:41:00,040 --> 00:41:01,480
whatever happens!

816
00:41:01,480 --> 00:41:02,760
Why did he just let it go?

817
00:41:02,760 --> 00:41:05,120
That's courting trouble.

818
00:41:05,720 --> 00:41:09,000
Chamberlain, maybe His Majesty has his concerns.

819
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,720
What concerns can he have?

820
00:41:12,640 --> 00:41:14,880
How much did he favor Eshan?

821
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:16,680
And so many begged for his mercy.

822
00:41:16,840 --> 00:41:19,320
In the end, he killed Eshan

823
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:21,040
without a blink.

824
00:41:25,720 --> 00:41:27,180
Hey, why are you smirking?

825
00:41:27,840 --> 00:41:28,770
No, not the same.

826
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:32,080
That depends on if that's a man or a woman.

827
00:41:32,080 --> 00:41:32,720
Woman.

828
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:35,160
Then it depends on if she's pretty

829
00:41:35,360 --> 00:41:36,560
or ugly.

830
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:37,800
She looks despicable.

831
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:39,200
When I think about her...

832
00:41:39,400 --> 00:41:41,000
Be careful. Be careful.

833
00:41:43,240 --> 00:41:44,880
What…what do you mean?

834
00:41:46,240 --> 00:41:47,720
If I think about it again,

835
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:49,880
she's good-looking.

836
00:41:50,200 --> 00:41:51,280
You mean..?

837
00:41:52,200 --> 00:41:54,330
Impossible! Absolutely impossible!

838
00:41:54,680 --> 00:41:55,480
Chamber Li,

839
00:41:55,720 --> 00:41:56,960
the world is so vast.

840
00:41:57,120 --> 00:41:59,050
How could anything be impossible?

841
00:41:59,880 --> 00:42:00,440
You…

842
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:05,560
You think I don’t know what His Majesty is thinking?

843
00:42:05,560 --> 00:42:08,080
If I say it's impossible, it's impossible.

844
00:42:08,920 --> 00:42:10,760
Then it's impossible. Impossible.

845
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:13,890
I shouldn’t have guessed what His Majesty was thinking.

846
00:42:17,520 --> 00:42:18,280
Impossible.

847
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:24,600
You killed it?

848
00:42:24,640 --> 00:42:26,370
It ruined my master’s banquet.

849
00:42:27,240 --> 00:42:29,080
I beat it up to vent my anger.

850
00:42:30,200 --> 00:42:31,130
Then I killed it.

851
00:42:32,240 --> 00:42:33,240
Where's the meat?

852
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:35,610
I meant to send it to the Royal Restaurant.

853
00:42:36,560 --> 00:42:37,400
But I heard

854
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:40,120
before our ancestors crossed Shanhaiguan,

855
00:42:40,120 --> 00:42:42,080
people of all banners lived on hunting

856
00:42:42,080 --> 00:42:43,400
and befriended hunting dogs.

857
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:45,840
So since the days of Taizu,

858
00:42:45,840 --> 00:42:47,680
it has been forbidden to eat dog meat.

859
00:42:47,680 --> 00:42:49,480
Though Snowball was killed by order of His Majesty,

860
00:42:49,480 --> 00:42:50,600
we couldn’t eat it.

861
00:42:51,400 --> 00:42:52,400
I was so angry

862
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:55,410
that I decided to bury it right then and there.

863
00:42:55,480 --> 00:42:56,160
Later,

864
00:42:56,880 --> 00:42:59,400
I remembered I need to preserve evidence for you.

865
00:42:59,400 --> 00:43:00,930
So I delivered the fur here.

866
00:43:03,840 --> 00:43:04,400
Alright.

867
00:43:05,200 --> 00:43:06,560
Then you can keep it.

868
00:43:06,840 --> 00:43:09,440
If Eunuch Li asks about it, I will answer to him.

869
00:43:09,440 --> 00:43:10,840
Thank you, Officer.
